          "process_md": "&amp;gt; **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** The applicant may visit and apply online at the [I-Khedut](https://ikhedut.gujarat.gov.in/) Portal.\n**Step 2:** Click on &amp;amp;#39;Login&amp;amp;#39; from the top right-hand side, then click on &amp;amp;quot;Beneficiary Registration&amp;amp;quot; and select any one from the &amp;amp;#39;Farmer&amp;amp;#39; or &amp;amp;#39;Institutional&amp;amp;#39; or &amp;amp;#39;Except For the Farmer&amp;amp;#39; as the Beneficiary Type.\n**Step 3:** Select the District, Taluka, and Village, choose &amp;amp;#39;what type of account holder you are?&amp;amp;#39;, enter your Account Number and Name, solve the Captcha, and click &amp;amp;#39;Save and Next&amp;amp;#39;.\n**Step 4:** Enter your Mobile Number and Email address, click &amp;amp;#39;Send OTP&amp;amp;#39;, enter the received OTP, create and confirm a Password, solve the Captcha, and click &amp;amp;#39;Submit&amp;amp;#39;.\n&amp;gt; **Login Process:** \n\n**Step 1:** The applicant may visit and apply online at the [I-Khedut](https://ikhedut.gujarat.gov.in/site/) Portal.\n**Step 2:** Click on &amp;amp;#39;Login&amp;amp;#39; from the top right-hand side of the homepage. On the home page, click on ‘Schemes’ and then click on ‘Agricultural Schemes’.\n**Step 3:** Now select the scheme, click on the ‘Apply’ button, and an application page will open.\n**Step 4:** Click on the &amp;amp;quot;Apply New&amp;amp;quot; button and submit a new application.\n**Step 5:** Click on the &amp;amp;quot;Update Application&amp;amp;quot; button to add corrections to the application.\n**Step 6:** Once the application is done, confirm it.\n**Step 7:** Take a printout of the confirmed application.\n&amp;gt; **Contact Us:** [Click here](https://ikhedut.gujarat.gov.in/Public/frm_Public_Contacts.aspx)\n\n<br>\n\n"
        }
